description: Defines the FinetuneResult entity class representing the outcome of a fine-tuning job, including related metadata and database mappings.

classes.name: FinetuneResult
classes.description: Java entity class for storing results of a fine-tuning process, mapped to 'finetune_results' table.

methods.name: FinetuneResult
methods.description: Parameterized constructor accepting FinetuneJob, Dataset, modelName, artifactPath, metricsPath.

methods.name: getId
methods.description: Returns the ID of the result.

methods.name: getModelName
methods.description: Returns the model name associated with the result.

methods.name: getArtifactPath
methods.description: Returns the path to the model artifact.

methods.name: getMetricsPath
methods.description: Returns the path to the metrics data.
